## 6. Learning and Skill Growth Tracker

This is very important for you because you said AI is making your coding skills weak and you want to become powerful again.

Add a **Developer Growth Mode**.

Features:

| Feature                | Purpose                                       |
| ---------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Daily coding challenge | One Laravel/PHP problem daily                 |
| Mistake tracker        | Record what you got wrong                     |
| Weak area detection    | Auth, queues, testing, transactions, security |
| Review score           | 1–10 score per task                           |
| Learning roadmap       | What to learn next                            |
| Code review journal    | Save lessons from PRs                         |

Example:

> Today’s Laravel Drill: Build idempotent webhook handler
> Weakness found: transaction locking
> Next topic: `lockForUpdate()` and deadlock retry handling

This could become one of the most powerful features of your app.

