This is where your app can become very powerful.

AI can help with:

| AI Feature      | Example                                  |
| --------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Daily planning  | “Plan my day based on my tasks”          |
| Task breakdown  | “Break this project into steps”          |
| Weekly review   | “What did I fail to complete this week?” |
