## 13. Decision Journal

This is underrated but very useful.

Whenever you make an important decision, record:

| Field            | Example                     |
| ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| Decision         | Use Bridge for payment rail |
| Reason           | Faster integration          |
| Risk             | Webhook reliability         |
| Expected outcome | Better deposit flow         |
| Review date      | After 30 days               |

Later the app asks:

> Was this decision correct?

This improves your judgment over time.

## 14. Weekly Review System

Every Sunday or Monday, the app should ask:

> What did you complete?
> What did you delay?
> What wasted your time?
> What caused stress?
> What should be improved next week?

Then it generates:

> Weekly productivity score
> Financial summary
> Habit score
> Missed commitments
> Recommended plan for next week

## 15. Focus Mode

A feature to help you work deeply.

Features:

| Feature            | Purpose                 |
